title: Episode 49: Tip Toeing

description:
Our pal Christine visits us from New York.

Bobby offers up his child to MJ.

Khalyla prefers full bush.

Gilbert mediates urban hour.

We talk thigh biting, a rash from Elton John, and a Mexican redhead albino dwarf thug.

 

Recorded July 11, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee
